name: Anti-Goatse
description: The Goatse singularity was inevitable, but with Anti-Goatse, I no longer fear it. Now I fear nothing... How does Goatse Maximus coexist with Anti- Goatse? While we fully support the systematic takeover of memetic culture and the power of memetic religions we must remind everyone that there is a balance to everything. Our job as the Order of Anti-Goastse is work with the Gospel of Goatse to provide a balanced digital ecosystem. Both are essential in the larger scope of memetic religion. In chaos, we find our calm; in memes, we find our balance. Tokenomics - Buy Tax - 0 % - Sell Tax - 0 % - 100 % Liquidity Pool is Burnt - Contract Ownership Renounced.
